point of beginning; containing an area of TWO THOUSAND THREE HUNDRED TWELVE (2,312) SQUARE METERS. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground by P.S. Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings true, This lot was surveyed in accordance with law and existing regulations promulgated thereunder by Jaime M. Maglana, Geodetic Engineer, on December 14, 1984, and was approved on January 11, 1985.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila this 1st day of September, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and eighty-eight.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) CATALINO MACARAIG, JR. Executive Secretary

